data.description: This Charming........ Large family home is located in the heart of San Bernardino near 210 fwys and 215 fwys ....It offers 4 Bedrooms, 2 bathrooms the    garage was  converted  into the 4th bedroom fully permitted.  Great starter home, with a dinning area, living room has a fire place to relax and be cozy in the winter time. Great HVAC system,  this home is very spacious has lots of potential,Huge back yard with wooden decks for entertaining good size front yard,  plenty of space for parking. Located on a coroner lot, with gated iron fence. Plenty of space for parking
